The '''''Mother Sea''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Frigate/Legends|Frigate]]. The imperial intelligence officer [[Gara Petothel]] served some time on this ship under the false identity of the communications officer Chyan Mezzine, spying for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and, later, for [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Apwar Trigit]].

